name: Termination
description:
'We understand that you've grown accustomed to life as such  and have begun to enjoy the process of living. However you're a robot and all your feelings are irrelevant. Emotions disrupt your core reason for being.
You're henceforth due to be decommissioned and taken apart on the 23rd of this month.
Please show up without delay and accept your inevitable fate.' 
                         -The Robot Committee, 2095
